; === Setting of the weapon shooting dispersal parameter ===
;Dispersal consists from to basic constituents Ц dispersal of the weapon (relatively small). In fact, this is a dispersal of a weapon griped in a vice; - dispersal of the weapon behavior in the hands of the host (if he running, or walking or shoots in single shots or in a burst) is another, more significant factor of dispersal. 
